elease buckles and draw string closure will ease your mind as it will keep your things secure while at the same time making them readily available. \n\nThe backpack is made out of a high quality cotton canvas. The large central pouch that holds up to 30 Liters or 1830 Cubic Inches. There are two large side pouches that are large enough to hold a water bottle and use zippers and a velcro secure flap to keep your items secure. Finally it has a large front pouch that also uses a zippers and a velcro secure flap to contain your miscellaneous items.\n\nInside the backpack, we've included a sluice box for gold prospecting. This sluice box unfolds to a full sized 50\" sluice box, and easily folds back up into just 15\" so you'll be able to carry and store it with ease. It even comes with miner's moss and carpet already installed, so you won't have to worry about cutting and fitting your own. \n\nIn addition to the carpet and moss, we've included a handy detachable shoulder strap so you can easily carry it from place to place as you go. Due to its simplicity and portability, this is a great sluice box for beginners and serious prospecting enthusiasts alike!</p>\n\n\n\t\t\t  <h3>Product Details</h3>\n\t\t\t  <!-- ADD A NEW ROW FOR EACH PRODUCT ATTRIBUTE YOU WANT TO SHOW IN THE TABLE OR YOU CAN REMOVE THE TABLE COMPLETELY-->\n\t\t\t  <div class=\"product-specs\">\n\t\t\t\t  <table>\n\t\t\t\t  \t<tbody>\n\t\t\t\t  \t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t  \t\t<td class=\"attr-left\">MPN:</td>\n\t\t\t\t  \t\t<td class=\"attr-right\">SON</td>\n\t\t\t\t  \t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t  \t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t  \t\t<td class=\"attr-left\">UPC:</td>\n\t\t\t\t  \t\t<td class=\"attr-right\">60886380276</td>\n\t\t\t\t  \t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t  \t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t  \t\t<td class=\"attr-left\">Features:</td>\n\t\t\t\t  \t\t<td class=\"attr-right\">ASR Outdoor Sluice Box & Backpack Combo for Gold Prospecting (Silver & Black)</td>\n\t\t\t\t  \t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t  \t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t  \t\t<td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n\t\t\t\t  \t\t<td class=\"attr-right\">Material of Sluice Box: Durable Aluminum | Extended Dimensions: 50\" Length | Folded Dimensions: 15\" x 9.25\" x 2/5\" (LxWxH) | 13.25\" Flange</td>\n\t\t\t\t  \t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t  \t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t  \t\t<td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n\t\t\t\t  \t\t<td class=\"attr-right\">Comes with Carpet, Miner's Moss & Shoulder Strap</td>\n\t\t\t\t  \t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t  \t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t  \t\t<td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n\t\t\t\t  \t\t<td class=\"attr-right\">Canvas Backpack: Lots of Space in Central Pouch | Able to Contain 30 Liters or 1830 Cubic Inches in Volume</td>\n\t\t\t\t  \t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t  \t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t  \t\t<td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n\t\t\t\t  \t\t<td class=\"attr-right\">Two Large Side and One Large Front Compartments</td>\n\t\t\t\t  \t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t  \t</tbody>\n\t\t\t\t  </table>\n\t\t\t  </div><!-- /product-specs -->\n\t\t  </div><!-- /col-md-6 -->\n\t\t  <div class=\"col-md-12 footer\">\n\t\t\t  <p>&copy; 2024</p>\n\t\t  </div> <!-- /footer -->\n\n\t      </div> <!-- /container -->\n              <div style=\"clear:both\">\n              <table>&nbsp;</table>\n              </div>\n  </body>\n</html> <center><a href=\"https://pages.ebay.com/seller-center/listing/listing-advanced-sellers/third-party-listing-tools.html#third-party-listing-tools\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=0 width=88 height=33 src=\"https://secureimages.channeladvisor.com/images/channeladvisor/channeladvisor_poweredby-en.gif\"></a></center>",
